Name: Fuel Cell Dispatch Manual

Caption.String: For fuel cell front-of-meter applications, battery charging from the grid is disabled.

Choose Manual Dispatch above to enable the manual dispatch model, then check boxes to allow the battery to discharge, fuel cell to run, or battery to discharge for each dispatch period. Use your mouse to select periods in the schedule matrices and your keyboard to type period numbers.
